ActCanadian Security Intelligence Service Act
PrecisAppointment of DALE NEUFELD of Ottawa, Ontario, to act as Director of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service, to hold office during pleasure until such time as a Director is appointed, for a term not exceeding six months, effective May 31, 2004.
